    "description": "探索这片危险与机遇并存、广阔而瑰丽、令人神往的新天地。你将作为经历海难的探险家，踏足不可思议的永恒岛，为自己书写崭新的命运。在岛上的荒野和废墟中，无穷无尽的战斗、觅食和锻造机会在等待着你。在无职业实时战斗系统中，引导超自然力量，或掌控致命武器；独自战斗，进入小队，或加入PvP团队参与 PvP 战斗——所有决定都由你做主。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特性:</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/a245242c67d841782f850a8b4c48d4f9.poster.avif?t=1768500124\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/a245242c67d841782f850a8b4c48d4f9.webm?t=1768500124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/a245242c67d841782f850a8b4c48d4f9.mp4?t=1768500124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>尽情探索永恒岛</strong><br>千百年来，永恒岛一直是奇幻传说的源头——如今，你已经找到了这座奇岛。你遭遇海难，没有物资，孤立无援，必须在这个所有规则都遭到超自然力量改变的世界中，克服重重险阻，努力前进。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/6d55bea9e6f1bf578ddd95fa3f46f68b.poster.avif?t=1768500124\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/6d55bea9e6f1bf578ddd95fa3f46f68b.webm?t=1768500124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/6d55bea9e6f1bf578ddd95fa3f46f68b.mp4?t=1768500124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>随心畅玩</strong><br>可以单人游戏，也可以跨平台组队游玩，或在各种 PvP 战斗中与敌人正面交锋。自定义角色的外观、技能和能力，尝试不同的流派，找出最适合你的游戏风格。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/5277b5abd2e9334557563ea9ac04c5db.poster.avif?t=1768500124\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/5277b5abd2e9334557563ea9ac04c5db.webm?t=1768500124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/5277b5abd2e9334557563ea9ac04c5db.mp4?t=1768500124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>剑、枪炮与巫术</strong><br>用残暴近战武器、掌控远程火炮或超自然力量武装自己，投身于 New World 的无职业实时动作战斗系统。随着游戏进展，你可以自主决定游戏体验——是化身冲锋陷阵的护阵坚盾？还是成为远距吟咒的团队后援？一切由你抉择。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/b4e506e4be5fa0732da63190fdb94e62.poster.avif?t=1768500124\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/b4e506e4be5fa0732da63190fdb94e62.webm?t=1768500124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/b4e506e4be5fa0732da63190fdb94e62.mp4?t=1768500124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>玩法由你决定</strong><br>从七种各具特色的初始原型中选择。从强大的杀戮机器，挥动巨斧和战锤残忍消灭敌人的毁灭者，到既是学者、也是战士，探求生与死之力的神秘修士：每种原型都有自己的独特玩法。你可以在游戏中随时选择和切换原型。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/73004f2e0b37b2a302c81552be3d5c67.poster.avif?t=1768500124\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/73004f2e0b37b2a302c81552be3d5c67.webm?t=1768500124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063730/extras/73004f2e0b37b2a302c81552be3d5c67.mp4?t=1768500124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>召唤坐骑</strong><br>驾驭骏马、恶狼与雄狮。每只坐骑均拥有独特外观和可染色装备，并且支持自定义命名。提升你的骑术技能等级，还可获得坐骑速度提升、增益效果和高阶坐骑补给食物等成长性奖励。<br><br><br><br><strong>辅助功能:</strong><br>在开始游戏之前，利用辅助设置功能，定制你的私人体验。根据你的喜好调整音频设置，调节音量大小，设置单声道、立体声和环绕声。通过键位绑定选项，个性化更改相机舒适度、游戏字幕和输入方式。最后，使用聊天文字转语音和语音转文字功能，确保绝不错过任何消息。<br>",
